  "texts": [
    "This enables us to create p2p similarity measures for large patent datasets.",
    "While the usefulness of text-based p2p similarity measures has been manifold demonstrated for applications such as semantic search, patent landscaping, technology mapping, and patent quality evaluation (cf. e.g.",
    "Hain et al., 2020; Arts et al., 2018 Arts et al.,, 2021)), we furthermore demonstrate that our transformer-based p2p similarity can be used for state-of-the-art automated patent classification.",
